scene.message:
Dark Girl: Aaah!{nl}
You're the ones who{nl}
got in Papa's way!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Put the school back{nl}
the way it was!{nl}
Or I'll spank your bottom{nl}
till it's twice the size!{waitkey}{ret}

Dark Girl: No waaay~{nl}
Aki only listens to{nl}
what Papa says!{waitkey}Try it if you can,{nl}
you flat-chested cow!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Flat...?!{nl}
Now I'm really mad!{nl}
What a hateful little brat!!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Easy, Sonomura.{nl}
She's just a kid.{nl}
Let's talk some sense{nl}
into her, all right...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: ...{wait_fr:108}{nl}
Why you!{nl}
You little brat~!{waitkey}{ret}

Aki: You're so noisy!{nl}
This is perfect{nl}
just die right here!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Mark!{nl}
This is no time to{nl}
be playing around!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hey!{nl}
Something weird{nl}
just showed up!{waitkey}{ret}
